{"tid":24483,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[赤龍船長]今日去見囡囡","createTime":"2016-12-05T14:25:05.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-05T15:05:26.000Z","uid":37701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"68292f88b896f9db5aa0db3787cf6f09c24cd855","tid":24483,"uid":37701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T14:25:05.000Z","msg":"上次沈左船之後，個心囉囉巒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n尋日忍唔住上左去 <br />\n為左俾個驚喜佢，我煮左飯扲上大陸俾佢食 <br />\n我煮左生炒骨，腐乳通菜同牛仔骨上去 <br />\n過關果陣好驚俾人捉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去到去骨場揾佢，佢唔認得我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n入到房，我拎啲飯出黎果陣佢嚇到走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n各位ching應該點算好？我真係好鍾意佢"},{"pid":"b6fc153abaaa8a1b9e2d165f097cf7a68fcd30d6","tid":24483,"uid":37701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T14:25:17.000Z","msg":"唔知赤龍巴打仍然在世嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1d0b2581b618a4e200045cd9cf6aac7f0718370","tid":24483,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T14:54:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知赤龍巴打仍然在世嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n結左婚啦"},{"pid":"6859c22ba8f3ea23f7fafb7463c47b9f6f94e296","tid":24483,"uid":43647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T15:05:26.000Z","msg":"煮飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}